  [Document Changes]
    * Added the following doc.

      =head1 Library Dependencies
      
      On Windows, the C<wsock32> and C<ws2_32> libraries are needed.
      if ($^O eq 'MSWin32') {
        $config->add_libs('wsock32', 'ws2_32');
      }
